dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Enhanced 911 and general mapping purposes.]
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents roads for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2011. [Line centerline map features of the roads within Polk County Wisconsin. Each segment of the road includes the road name, address ranges, road code, and zip code.]
